gomodel:SYNGO_1163  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: By application of cryoimmunogold labelling on rat cerebellum sections, Koh et al demonstrate that HPC-1 is localized on plasma membrane and synaptic vesicles of presynaptic boutons which form synapses with Purkenje cells (Fig. 3 and Fig. 11).\n\n2/9/2017 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Information is in the figure legends and in the title of the article." , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
